<h2>懶人包</h2>

<ul>
<li><p>第一次更新
<code>
sudo apt update &amp;&amp; sudo apt install aptitude &amp;&amp; sudo aptitude upgrade -y --full-resolve
</code></p></li>
<li><p>更新
<code>
sudo apt update &amp;&amp; sudo aptitude upgrade -y --full-resolve &amp;&amp; sudo apt autoremove
